data.description: This beautifully home has been remodeled and offers 4-bedrooms, 2-full bathrooms, a spacious family room with a cozy fireplace and an oversize sunroom with modern upgrades throughout! Step inside and be greeted by the spacious living and dining rooms with a practical door that connects to the kitchen and breakfast area. The kitchen oversees the breakfast and family rooms making this home a perfect place to entertain. The primary suite has an updated bathroom with new granite vanity, sink, mirrors and light fixtures. This home offers the perfect blend of modern updates and practical comfort in a great location, minutes from the airport and easy access to 410 and I35.
